Exercise 3 - Greet Endpoint using Spring Boot

📄 Description:
A modified version of the REST controller to greet users using a custom endpoint.

🧪 Sample Input:
GET request to:
http://localhost:8080/greet

✅ Output:
Hello from Spring Boot!

⚙️ What’s Used:
- @RestController & @GetMapping
- Spring Boot Web Starter
- Embedded Tomcat on port 8080
